<h1 class='property-title'>transition-delay</h1>
<p class='property-description'>The<code> transition-delay </code><a title="CSS" rel="internal" href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en/CSS">CSS</a> property specifies the amount of time to wait between a change being requested to a property that is to be transitioned and the start of the <a title="en/CSS/CSS transitions" rel="internal" href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en/CSS/CSS_transitions">transition effect</a>.</p>